end\": 1890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"a group effort\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"whose Beyonce-inspired floor routine locked victory\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles's finishing touch\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US finished with a score of 171.296, almost six clear of their nearest rivals Italy.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.8317301271364719, \"rank\": 0.2019855174144788, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9141007191600662, \"rank\": 0.09397052918191795, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"their nearest rivals\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil took an emotional bronze, the first Olympic team medal in their history, but it was to Britain's cost, losing out in fourth by just 0.034 despite some stellar performances through the evening, particularly Alice Kinsella's near-immaculate floor.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9991185690602935, \"rank\": 0.000879619443376314, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9962074884321841, \"rank\": 0.0038069341532296487, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an emotional bronze\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Olympic team medal\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"their history\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"some stellar performances\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But no one could touch the Americans.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"the Americans\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world had come to see Biles win gold: queues fed back to the Seine as fans and VIPs arrived to witness her talent in the flesh.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2423, \"end\": 2428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999998321982, \"rank\": 1.6794462636614507e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2398}, {\"ngram\": \"queues\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"VIPs\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2445}, {\"ngram\": \"her talent\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"the flesh\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serena Williams and Bill Gates took their seats.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serena Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 2510, \"end\": 2520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Gates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.865297568205996e-34, \"text\": \"Bill Gates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Gates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Gates\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their seats\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Backstage, inside the call room, Biles led her team through some stretches and had a sincere conversation with her coach.\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the call room\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"her team\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"some stretches\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"a sincere conversation\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watching on, it felt like this was the real Biles: no smile for the camera, no wave to her adoring public.\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the real Biles\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"the camera\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"her adoring public\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She looked understandably nervous.\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She looked almost normal.\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And perhaps the entire night revealed another side of Biles.\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the entire night\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"another side\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is the best, of course, and watching her launch her body at the vault is both terrifying and thrilling in equal measure.\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"equal measure\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she is also human.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She wobbled on the beam just a touch and the audience gasped.\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beam\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3062}, {\"ngram\": \"just a touch\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She played it safe, for her, on the vault and uneven bars too.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vault and uneven bars\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her mesmerising floor routine contained little falls which teetered out of bounds.\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her mesmerising floor routine\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"little falls\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"bounds\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will probably win much more this week and she will make gymnastics look easy, so it is worth taking this moment to remember: it is not, and her journey has not been.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"her journey\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The word redemption has been used a lot this week to describe Biles's Games, but redemption requires sin: this gold medal was not redemption but an act of liberation, freeing herself from others' expectations, from external pressure, from the judgement of anonymous social media accounts, from the organisations that failed to protect her and her fellow victims of sexual abuse, from the hold that abuse had over her mental and physical self.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The word redemption\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3437}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles's Games\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3493}, {\"ngram\": \"redemption\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3509}, {\"ngram\": \"sin\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3522}, {\"ngram\": \"this gold medal\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"redemption\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3558}, {\"ngram\": \"an act\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"liberation\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3583}, {\"ngram\": \"others' expectations\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"external pressure\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"the judgement\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3670}, {\"ngram\": \"anonymous social media accounts\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3705}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisations\", \"from\": 3712, \"to\": 3729}, {\"ngram\": \"her fellow victims\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3779}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual abuse\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3795}, {\"ngram\": \"the hold\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3810}, {\"ngram\": \"abuse\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3821}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental and physical self\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She called therapy her \\\"fifth rotation\\\" in training, as important as practising the bars or the beam.\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"her \\\"fifth rotation\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 3900}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"the bars\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"the beam\", \"from\": 3954, \"to\": 3962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the US team landed in Antwerp for the World Championships last year, her friends went out to find chocolate ice cream while Biles stayed in her hotel and spent two hours speaking to her therapist on Zoom.\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 4173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3973, \"end\": 3975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.8317301271364719, \"rank\": 0.2019855174144788, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3991, \"end\": 3998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\", \"score\": 0.9999998982543782, \"rank\": 1.017356728916872e-07, \"text\": \"Antwerp\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4026}, {\"ngram\": \"her friends\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4049}, {\"ngram\": \"chocolate ice cream\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4086}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4098}, {\"ngram\": \"her hotel\", \"from\": 4109, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"two hours\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4138}, {\"ngram\": \"her therapist\", \"from\": 4151, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"Zoom\", \"from\": 4168, \"to\": 4172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has slowly rebuilt herself and she has done it with the help and support of her teammates, in training and in competition.\", \"from\": 4175, \"to\": 4301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the help\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4239}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\": 4255, \"to\": 4268}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 4273, \"to\": 4281}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was with her team that Biles first suffered the twisties in Tokyo and uttered that now famous speech, said through a mask while holding back the tears.\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4365, \"end\": 4370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999996614120055, \"rank\": 3.323501755554059e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her team\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4322}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4333}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4361}, {\"ngram\": \"now famous speech\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4405}, {\"ngram\": \"a mask\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4426}, {\"ngram\": \"the tears\", \"from\": 4446, \"to\": 4455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sorry, I love you guys, but you are gonna be just fine,\\\" she told them before leaving the floor.\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you guy